General.Name: Weihai Baihe Biology Technological Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Weihai Baihe Biology Technological Co., Ltd. engages in manufacture and sale of nutrition and healthy food in China and internationally. The company offers health foods, sports nutrition products, and foods for special dietary uses. It offers its products in the form of soft capsules, hard capsules, tablets, powders, oral liquids, drops, and bottles. The company also exports its products to approximately 70 countries and regions. Weihai Baihe Biology Technological Co., Ltd. was founded in 1996 and is based in Rongcheng, China.
